records.addlTxt:
Defendant Lashaunda Marie Rimmer not in court.  Prosecuting attorney Jack T Eichorst in court for the State of Wisconsin. 
Defendant failing to appear, Court ordered an Arrest Warrant to be issued. Upon arrest, defendant is ordered remanded to a commissioner. Court ordered any bail on deposit to be forfeited. Court makes a finding that there is a possible victim identified and stays the forfeiture order with restitution to be determined at close of case.
Summons mailed.  Defendant ordered into room 221 Safety Building on 9/12/22 @ 1p
Actual Date Bond Posted with Milwaukee County Sheriff  on 07/24/2022
Defendant is Out-of-Custody. Court appearance in Out-Of-Custody Court, Room 221 Safety Building on 9-12-2022 @1p
